name: CYBRO
description: CYBRO is an earn marketplace on Blast L2. CYBRO acts as an aggregator and a platform for different investment options with different levels of risk, interest rates, and investment periods. The instruments include staking, farming, and lending. CYBRO is built using the mechanism of vaults, grouped for different types of users and assets. CYBRO focuses on the ease of topping up and withdrawing, along with the seamless investment process. The launch is expected in Q2'2024.
